-- Russian Billionaire Fridman’s Alfa Forms Nickel Venture in Cuba
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2010-09-24T08:00:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-24/russian-billionaire-fridman-s-alfa-forms-venture-to-produce-nickel-in-cuba.html
Russian billionaire  Mikhail
Fridman ’s Alfa Group said it formed a joint venture in Cuba to
extract nickel from industrial waste, the Moscow-based company’s
A1 unit said in a statement today.  Cuban President Raul Castro approved Alfa’s venture with
the state-run company Commercial Caribbean Nickel SA, A1 said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
